        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "Divine protection helps protect your companions. You and your allies gain a +1 status bonus to AC while within the emanation. Once per round on subsequent turns, you can Sustain the spell to increase the emanation\u2019s radius by 10 feet. Benediction can counteract *malediction*.",
